criteria.textblock:
        Exclusion Criteria:

        The following patients will be excluded:

          1. Patients below the age of 18 years and above 60 years as this study is not on children
             or older patients;

          2. Patients who can't move their hands and eyes/or can't perform basic movements;

          3. Patients who are unconscious for longer periods and unable to recover consciousness;

          4. Patients not meeting the basic screening criteria of PTSD/ PTSD is not the main
             problem;

          5. Patients with severe intellectual impairments, since such patients are difficult to
             communicate.
